lio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.09.32-PM-300x244.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"244\" /></a>\r\n\r\nNaturally, at that point, I did what any normal person would do: Turn on my webcam...\r\n\r\nJust kidding. After immediately deleting poor Virginia from my gchat I realized something. Virginia was probably a computer. I was probably talking to some server. After that, I got really depressed because I didn\'t test out the program, see how smart it was, see what it would respond back.\r\n\r\nAnd today... a miracle happened:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.10-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1600\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2014-01-06 at 9.11.10 PM\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.10-PM.png\" width=\"552\" height=\"657\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWhen she said the \"bot???\" I started to think that maybe she wasn\'t a computer.\r\n\r\n<a style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\" href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.16-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1599\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2014-01-06 at 9.11.16 PM\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.16-PM.png\" width=\"552\" height=\"657\" /></a>\r\n\r\nShe responded to my questions. She\'s real! ... what a disappointment.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.25-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1598\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2014-01-06 at 9.11.25 PM\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.25-PM.png\" width=\"552\" height=\"657\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe spam comment was pretty hilarious and pretty smart, but it was all downhill form there...\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.33-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1597\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2014-01-06 at 9.11.33 PM\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.33-PM.png\" width=\"552\" height=\"657\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAt this point, anyone would be pretty convinced. I\'m ashamed it took me so long.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.40-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1596\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2014-01-06 at 9.11.40 PM\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.40-PM.png\" width=\"552\" height=\"657\" /></a>\r\n\r\nShe never responded back... Maybe someday Juliet will talk to me again....','Conversations with a Robot?','','publish','open','open','','conversations-robot','','','2014-01-23 04:36:23','2014-01-23 04:36:23','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?p=1592',0,'post','',0),(1593,1,'2014-01-07 02:10:05','2014-01-07 02:10:05','','Screen Shot 2014-01-03 at 11.31.54 PM','','inherit','open','open','','screen-shot-2014-01-03-at-11-31-54-pm','','','2014-01-07 02:10:05','2014-01-07 02:10:05','',1592,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-03-at-11.31.54-PM.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1594,1,'2014-01-07 02:10:31','2014-01-07 02:10:31','','Screen Shot 2014-01-06 at 9.09.32 PM','','inherit','open','open','','screen-shot-2014-01-06-at-9-09-32-pm','','','2014-01-07 02:10:31','2014-01-07 02:10:31','',1592,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.09.32-PM.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1595,1,'2014-01-07 02:29:20','2014-01-07 02:29:20','','Screen Shot 2014-01-06 at 9.11.46 PM','','inherit','open','open','','screen-shot-2014-01-06-at-9-11-46-pm','','','2014-01-07 02:29:20','2014-01-07 02:29:20','',1592,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-06-at-9.11.46-PM.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(15