ody>\r\n</table>\r\nI would then upload my CSV and it would tell me if it send out the emails or not.\r\n\r\nPretty useful.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000080;\"><a href=\"http://thejsj.com/uncategorized/email-sender-wordpress-plugin/attachment/emailsender-php/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1332\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\">emailSender.php</span></a></span>','Email Sender - Wordpress Plugin','','inherit','open','open','','1324-revision-v1','','','2014-01-23 02:02:02','2014-01-23 02:02:02','',1324,'http://localhost/~jorgesilva/2014/thejsj9/?p=1663',0,'revision','',0),(1668,1,'2013-02-12 04:08:48','2013-02-12 04:08:48','Today, I found my first publication. It\'s a paper titled “Design through the loop: Creating through programing in the field of graphic design”, talking about the intersections of design and programming.\r\n\r\nCheck it out in the publisher\'s website: <a href=\"http://www.blucher.com.br/livro.asp?Codlivro=06927\">http://www.blucher.com.br/livro.asp?Codlivro=06927</a>\r\n\r\nOr check out the PDF version: <a href=\"http://www.fau.usp.br/icdhs2012/files/ICDHS2012_designfrontiers-online_b.pdf\">http://www.fau.usp.br/icdhs2012/files/ICDHS2012_designfrontiers-online_b.pdf</a>. It\'s on page 353!','I Got Published? I Got Published!','','inherit','open','open','','1261-revision-v1','','','2013-02-12 04:08:48','2013-02-12 04:08:48','',1261,'http://localhost/~jorgesilva/2014/thejsj9/?p=1668',0,'revision','',0),(1670,1,'2014-01-23 04:36:19','2014-01-23 04:36:19','','robot-chat','','inherit','open','open','','robot-chat','','','2014-01-23 04:36:19','2014-01-23 04:36:19','',1592,'http://localhost/~jorgesilva/2014/thejsj9/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/robot-chat.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1717,1,'2014-01-26 18:43:32','2014-01-26 18:43:32','These are some sketches I\'ve been working on about Spain. I\'m interested in Spain\'s recent economic crisis.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/uncategorized/spains-economic-crisis-visualization/attachment/thejsj-com-20